item.title: Faculty and staff well-beings
item.description: Wellness encompasses mental, spiritual, physical, financial, family and workplace health. Discover programs and resources available to support your wellness journey and improve well-being. (Access on UM Intranet with your @umanitoba.ca employee email address.)

item.title: Student health and wellness
item.description: Health and wellness play a critical role in student success. Explore a wide range of services that are available to you that support your physical and mental well-being.
